Uses of Class
Catalano.Core.FloatRange

  • Packages that use FloatRange 
    Package Description
    Catalano.Core
    The Catalano.Core contains common classes used by other namespaces of the framework and classes, which can be used independently for various purposes.
    Catalano.Imaging.Concurrent.Filters
    The Catalano.Imaging.Concurrent.Filters namespace contains collection classes, which provide different image processing filters running in parallel.
    Catalano.Imaging.Filters
    The Catalano.Imaging.Filters namespace contains collection classes, which provide different image processing filters.
    Catalano.Math
    The Catalano.Math namespace contains set of math utilities, which are used by other Catalano framework's namespaces or may be used individually.
    Catalano.Neuro
    The Catalano.Neuro namespace contains interfaces and classes for neural networks computations.
    Catalano.Statistics
    The Catalano.Statistics namespace contains set of statistics utilities, which are used by other Catalano framework's namespaces or may be used individually.
